      <title>俄罗斯炼油厂遭遇无人机破坏，气味弥漫城市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gas-odor-swamps-russian-city-as-refinery-deals-with-drone-damage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯阿斯特拉罕市居民抱怨称，在乌克兰无人机袭击后，大型天然气和凝析油炼油厂正在恢复运营，途中闻到强烈的工业气味。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/gas-odor-swamps-russian-city-as-refinery-deals-with-drone-damage</guid>
