    <item>
      <title>特朗普接管加沙的想法得到以色列支持，阿拉伯人反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-idea-for-us-takeover-of-gaza-stokes-middle-east-divisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普提出的减少加沙人口并接管加沙的想法在以色列受到广泛欢迎，官员们称赞这一意外提议是加强与哈马斯战争后安全的一种手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-idea-for-us-takeover-of-gaza-stokes-middle-east-divisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:22:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦将加强对俄罗斯影子舰队油轮的审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/denmark-to-intensify-scrutiny-of-russia-s-shadow-fleet-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦将加强对通过其狭窄海峡运输俄罗斯石油的船只的检查，以保护环境和海上安全，免受莫斯科影子舰队中老旧船只的侵害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/denmark-to-intensify-scrutiny-of-russia-s-shadow-fleet-tankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 13:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
